a:["$","pre",null,{"className":"my-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl bg-[#0F172A] p-5 text-sm","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"Gateway 唔 work？\n     │\n     ▼\nopenclaw gateway status 有冇輸出？\n     │\n  ┌──┴──┐\n 冇     有\n  │     │\n  ▼     ▼\nGateway  有冇黃色 warning？\n未跑     │\n  │   ┌──┴──┐\n  │  冇     有\n  │   │     │\n  ▼   │     ▼\nopenclaw  openclaw doctor\ngateway    --repair\n start     │\n  │        ▼\n  └──► 重試 gateway status\n         │\n         ▼\n     Port 18789 通唔通？\n         │\n      ┌──┴──┐\n     通    唔通\n      │     │\n      ▼     ▼\n  Auth 設   lsof -i :18789\n  咗未？    睇邊個佔用\n      │\n   ┌──┴──┐\n  設咗  未設\n   │     │\n   ▼     ▼\n ✅   openclaw config set\n  OK  gateway.auth.mode token\n"}]}]
